name: Let's Build a Mobile App Using React Native! Pt. 2!
description:
Join us this month (virtually) as Lucas Gladding continues developing an application using React Native! We'll again be working with TypeScript, and including tests using Jest and React Native Testing Library.

***Please note that we will be recording this meetup. If you wish to not be recorded, please mute your microphone, and disable your camera. We will not include the list of attendees in our recording.***

Don't forget, we'll be raffling for a 1 year subscription to any JetBrains product at every meetup!

Stay tuned for more details as we get closer to the meetup. Hoping all of you have been well during this time, and we look forward to seeing you! :)

Agenda:
6:30pm - 8:00pm: Presentation
8:00pm - 9pm: Q&A and Online Networking! (We'll explain how)
